Package: MyDataTools
Type: Package
Title: A Package for Loading and Plotting Data
Version: 0.1.2
Authors@R: 
    person("Przemyslaw", "Miskowiec", email = "przemekmiskowiec@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: The package maintainer <przemekmiskowiec@gmail.com>
Description: 
    MyDataTools is an R package designed to simplify the process of loading and visualizing datasets.
    The package provides two main functions, load_dataset() and autoplot(). 
    The load_dataset() function supports loading data from various file formats including CSV, Excel, and text files, 
    automatically detecting the file type and using the appropriate method to read the data into R.
    The autoplot() function leverages the powerful ggplot2 package to create customizable line, scatter, histograms and bar plots 
    with minimal code, enabling users to quickly visualize their data for analysis and presentation.
